&trans    &trans     &mkp RCLK       &mkp MCLK     &mkp LCLK       &trans                   &trans &trans &trans &trans &trans &trans
&trans    &trans     &mmv MOVE_LEFT  &mmv MOVE_UP  &mmv MOVE_DOWN  &mmv MOVE_RIGHT          &trans &trans &trans &trans &trans &trans
